Roundabout License - v 1.0
==================================

The Roundabout Mod is created to bring joy to others, it may be 
copied, modified, and shared as the users of the mod see fit.

As far as distribution is concerned, you may distribute your modifications
as you please, but you may not claim ownership of the mod. You must
respect the intentions of the original author, and honor any request
made by the author regarding distribution.

In any other circumstance, you have complete free reign to use, 
reuse, modify, and share code. Just make sure to credit the original
author and provide a link to the original mod if a significant amount
of code is used.
